__NAME__ purpose
specify directory for runtime files
__END__

__NAME__ synopsis
<arg choice='plain'><replaceable>directory</replaceable></arg>
__END__

__NAME__ example: Creating directory structure similar to a Linux filesystem
<programlisting>
RunDir var/run
</programlisting>
__END__

__NAME__ see also
PageDir, ProductDir, ScratchDir
__END__
